Text: "I traveled all around the world : Canada Usa Mexico Caribbean French Polynesia\
  \ Europe.\nEverytime is an aventure with myself and new people connection.\nI liked\
  \ to be out of control and be with my instinct. When you are not in your country,\
  \ you are like a children, everything is new: the lanscape, the food, the langage,\
  \ people, mysic, art....\nI'm a m\xE9dicinal plants lover, I love discover new plants\
  \ or flowers. I want to know all the medicine in the world to help people to be\
  \ in good health. Every countries have a past medicine with plants. Old people are\
  \ the better encyclopedy.\nYou can learn a lot with the gastronomy also,with the\
  \ diff\xE9rent spices.\nI think it'll be a good idea to write about it."
